                    "value": "<p>Without fully transforming your body, you gain one animalistic feature, which you select from the list below each time you Cast the Spell.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spell-effects.Spell Effect: Animal Feature (Cat Eyes)]{Cat Eyes}</strong> You gain Low-Light Vision.</li>\n<li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spell-effects.Spell Effect: Animal Feature (Claws)]{Claws}</strong> You gain a claw attack that deals 1d6 slashing damage and has the agile, finesse, and unarmed traits.</li>\n<li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spell-effects.Spell Effect: Animal Feature (Jaws)]{Jaws}</strong> You gain a jaws attack that deals 1d8 piercing damage and has the unarmed trait.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (4th)</strong> Add the following options to the list you can choose from.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spell-effects.Spell Effect: Animal Feature (Fish Tail)]{Fish Tail}</strong> You gain a Swim Speed equal to your land Speed.</li>\n<li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spell-effects.Spell Effect: Animal Feature (Owl Eyes)]{Owl Eyes}</strong> You gain Darkvision.</li>\n<li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spell-effects.Spell Effect: Animal Feature (Wings)]{Wings}</strong> You gain a Fly Speed equal to your land Speed.</li>\n</ul>"
